name: Vintage-inspired rayon seam binding - 6 yards in Portabello
description:
Just like the kind found in grandmother's sewing cabinet...

This silky smooth and oh-so dreamy rayon seam binding is perfect for pretty packages, works wonders on mixed-media, scrapbooking, cardmaking, and papercrafting projects, and is simply stunning when used with a variety of DIY wedding projects.

Details:
• 6 yards (18 feet)
• Color = Portabello
• Washable
• Woven-edge to prevent fraying
• Comes hand-wound and packaged
